{"article_id":"RLq1kxL3XnLwNL2z","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"In public testimony before Congress today , President Trump 's former attorney Michael Cohen is accusing the president of criminal conduct while in office .","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"Cohen ,","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"who 's been convicted of perjury","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"for lying to Congress ,","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"is telling Congress","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"that he thinks","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"Trump is a `` racist , '' a `` conman '' and a `` cheat . ''","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Cohen is sharing what he says","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"are details of President Trump 's alleged actions in reimbursements for payments","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"made to a porn star","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"to keep her quiet about an affair during the 2016 campaign .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"In his prepared testimony , Cohen says","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"the president directed him to make the payments","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"and paid him back over a period of several months","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"after he took office .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Congressional Democrats say","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"they 're seeking to identify","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"whether the actions are true .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Trump opponents say","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"that could be seen as a violation of campaign finance laws ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"granting liberals ground","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"to move toward impeachment .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Cohen is also accusing the president of having prior knowledge of the Wikileaks e-mail dump","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that damaged Hillary Clinton 's presidential campaign .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Cohen admits","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"he does not have any proof","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"the campaign colluded with Russia .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"He admits","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Trump did not directly tell him to lie ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"but he claims","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"that Trump `` would look me in the eye","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"and tell me","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"there 's no business in Russia","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"and then go out","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"and lie to the American people","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"by saying the same thing . ''","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"While being disbarred on Tuesday in New York as part of his deal with Robert Mueller ,","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"Cohen was in a private hearing with the House Intelligence Committee .","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"President Trump ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"who is in Hanoi for a summit with North Korea 's Kim Jong Un ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"is expected to watch the hearing","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"according to White House Officials .","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"In a tweet on Tuesday , President Trump condemned Cohen for his actions .","depth":4},{"id":43,"text":"`` Michael Cohen was one of many lawyers","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"who represented me","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"( unfortunately ) .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"He had other clients also .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"He was just disbarred by the State Supreme Court for lying & fraud , ''","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"wrote President Trump .","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"`` He did bad things","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"unrelated to Trump .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"He is lying","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"in order to reduce his prison time .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"Using Crooked 's lawyer ! ''","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"Michael Cohen was one of many lawyers","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"who represented me","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"( unfortunately ) .","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"He had other clients also .","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"He was just disbarred by the State Supreme Court for lying & fraud .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"He did bad things","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"unrelated to Trump .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"He is lying","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"in order to reduce his prison time .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Using Crooked 's lawyer !","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"February 27 , 2019","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"In November , Cohen pleaded guilty to lying to Congress in former testimony about Trump 's business dealings with Russia .","depth":4},{"id":68,"text":"The guilty plea stemmed from a 2017 testimony to the Senate Intelligence Committee","depth":5},{"id":69,"text":"in which Cohen gave a `` false '' account of an intended Trump Tower in Moscow .","depth":5},{"id":70,"text":"Cohen previously shared","depth":5},{"id":71,"text":"that communication with Russia ended before January 2016 ,","depth":5},{"id":72,"text":"but now he says","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"the talks continued into June 2016 .","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"Cohen , 52 , is expected to start his three-year prison sentence in May .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":149,"left":141,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":116,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":110,"right":115,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":110,"left":89,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":85,"right":88,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":81,"right":84,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":0,"right":80,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":78,"right":79,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":78,"left":77,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":77,"left":1,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":5,"